data.description: Discover modern living in this 4-bed, 2-bath CBS home built in 2021. With a spacious open concept and a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, the interior features new tile and laminate flooring, new paint throughout, an inviting island in the kitchen with staggered espresso cabinets & stainless steel appliances.  The exterior shines with new paint, gutters, and a 6' fence enclosing a beautiful back yard as well as a new screened in lanai to enjoy coffee or watch the sun rise.  Located in the desirable 34953 zip code, this centrally positioned home provides easy access to shopping, dining, hospitals, I-95, and the Turnpike for a fast & easy commute.  You don't want to miss this one!!
